(enablePrefetching, numRCQEntries).explanation: Enabling prefetching increases memory traffic and requires more request completion queue entries to handle the additional outstanding memory requests;

(enablePrefetching, power).explanation: Prefetching mechanisms consume additional power through increased memory accesses, cache activity, and logic operations;

(enablePrefetching, power_pad).explanation: Prefetching is a software/logic feature that does not directly affect the physical pad power consumption of the chip;
